long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Dad Jokes tells a new joke each time you open a new tab

Have a laugh and enjoy a modern online search experience simply by opening up a new tab in your browser.

Once you install this desktop extension, your browsers new tab will be replaced and show Microsoft Bing search results.
 
By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Dad Jokes Chrome extension and setting Chrome™️ New Tab search to that provided by the service with results by Microsoft Bing, and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. 

What are ‘Dad Jokes’ you might be asking? They’re those corny and often predictable type of wholesome joke told by many Fathers which are sometimes so silly and unfunny that they’re funny. Even hilarious. If that makes sense!!
 
Laugh, Search & be Happy!!
